data.description: 752 Eastview Ave. is on the market just for you. This beautiful home has 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, an open floor plan, 2 car integral garage, and much much more. Inside you will notice the pristine hardwood floors, that flow throughout the entire house. In the main living area there is a wood burning fireplace that would be perfect for the chilly nights. The master bedroom will leave you in aww, with a separate sitting area or you could make it into a walk-in closet, or even a nursery and still have plenty of room for your bedroom accessories. When going outside you will have a tiered deck that can be used for barbecues, reading, or relaxation. The yard could be a gardeners dream. With different shelves and elevations, this would be perfect for all types of plants and flowers.
